# ── Source Control ─────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# ── .NET Build Artifacts (rebuilt inside container) ───────────
**/bin
**/obj
**/TestResults
**/coverage
**/*.coverage
**/*.coveragexml

# ── Secrets & Environment ──────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Sensitive appsettings (injected via Docker environment vars)
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Production.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

# ── Project User & Local Files ─────────────────────────────────
**/*.*proj.user
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm
**/*.suo
**/*.user

# ── IDE & Editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.toolstarget

# ── Docker Files (not needed inside the image) ─────────────────
**/docker-compose*
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore

# ── Kubernetes / Helm / Azure ──────────────────────────────────
**/azds.yaml
**/charts
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml

# ── Docs & Repo Files ──────────────────────────────────────────
LICENSE
README.md
**/*.md

# ── OS Junk ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/Desktop.ini

# ── Logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.log
**/logs

# ── Keep these git refs (required for BuildKit layer caching) ──
!.git/HEAD
!.git/config
!.git/packed-refs
!.git/refs/heads/**